Class FractionImpl

java.lang.Object
HW1.FractionImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
Fraction, Comparable<Fraction>
public class FractionImpl extends Object implements Fraction
A class representing a fraction with an integer numerator and a positive integer denominator.
